    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the &quot;Don't Fret&quot; Audition Demo.   This is a demo that we released a year ago.  Please enjoy where the game was in 2024.   Don't Fret has come a long way from this initial demo and we are excited to release an updated version in the soon! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MEET FRET - THE LIVING INSTRUMENT</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202450/extras/d7bc2cb7fce08110a751913dd7542ea5.poster.avif?t=1761691961\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202450/extras/d7bc2cb7fce08110a751913dd7542ea5.webm?t=1761691961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202450/extras/d7bc2cb7fce08110a751913dd7542ea5.mp4?t=1761691961\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet Fret, a sentient guitar trapped in a nightmare of music and madness. Navigate the decaying halls of Harmonic Heights, uncover its secrets, and confront the horrors in a music world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A STYLIZED WORLD OF SOUND AND FEAR</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202450/extras/db3c373a492c024a820141d2e2c4c1fb.poster.avif?t=1761691961\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202450/extras/db3c373a492c024a820141d2e2c4c1fb.webm?t=1761691961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202450/extras/db3c373a492c024a820141d2e2c4c1fb.mp4?t=1761691961\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the visually stunning world of <i>Don’t Fret</i>, where every instrument, hallway, and shadow is alive with purpose. The game’s bold art direction blends psychological horror with musical surrealism, creating an unforgettable atmosphere that sets it apart from every other indie horror title. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>EXPLORE A MASSIVE, MUSICAL WORLD</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202450/extras/a1955ad2552a57644f6a07240728b68f.poster.avif?t=1761691961\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202450/extras/a1955ad2552a57644f6a07240728b68f.webm?t=1761691961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202450/extras/a1955ad2552a57644f6a07240728b68f.mp4?t=1761691961\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shattering the boundaries of traditional indie horror with an expansive world spanning dozens of handcrafted environments — from classrooms and underground tunnels to outside courtyards, gondola rides, and more. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every area in Harmonic Heights is designed to keep you engaged at every turn. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A CINEMATIC NARRATIVE EXPERIENCE</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202450/extras/cf365e56ae51be44caad8ae68487e4a2.poster.avif?t=1761691961\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202450/extras/cf365e56ae51be44caad8ae68487e4a2.webm?t=1761691961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202450/extras/cf365e56ae51be44caad8ae68487e4a2.mp4?t=1761691961\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Don’t Fret</i> delivers a story-driven horror experience that unfolds through audio logs, inspectable items, and cinematic cutscenes seamlessly woven into gameplay. Unravel a tale of exploitation, performance, and identity as you descend into the nightmare of Harmonic Heights</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>AN UNFORGETTABLE CAST </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202450/extras/476a70dd4571f923f079c2d7d2c77d64.poster.avif?t=1761691961\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202450/extras/476a70dd4571f923f079c2d7d2c77d64.webm?t=1761691961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202450/extras/476a70dd4571f923f079c2d7d2c77d64.mp4?t=1761691961\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The heart of <i>Don’t Fret</i> lies in its extraordinary cast. They deliver haunting, emotionally charged performances that pull players deep into the game’s unsettling world. Their authenticity and power don’t just tell the story - they shape the fear, tension, and humanity at its core.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thank you for giving Don't! Fret a shot. This is our first game and we are doing our best! We welcome feedback!</p>",
